---

<section id="about" class="mission">
  <div class="container mission-inner">
    <div class="mission-intro">
      <span class="mission-label" data-animate="fade-up">Our Purpose</span>
      <h2 class="mission-heading" data-animate="fade-up">
        We're a community of practice using emerging technologies for systems transformation.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mission-body-block" data-animate="fade-up">
      <p class="mission-body">
        SuperBenefit's mission is to develop the social and financial flywheels that enable the invention and acceleration of a better world; Strengthening capacities for systems innovation and supporting people to clarify pathways towards shared goals.
      </p>
      <p class="mission-body">
        Our work includes researching and incubating initiatives that harness emerging technologies and practices for decentralized coordination in pursuit of systems transformation.
      </p>
      <p class="mission-link">
        <!-- "About" link hidden until /about page is ready to launch -->
        <a href="/about" hidden>Read more about our mission &rarr;</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mission {
    background: var(--color-cream);
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl) 180px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .mission-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .mission-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-md);
  }

  .mission-heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 1.4rem + 1.75vw, 2.625rem);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .mission-body-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding-left: var(--space-xl);
    border-left: 1px solid rgb(var(--color-orange-rgb) / 0.3);
  }

  .mission-body {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.7;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .mission-link {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .mission-link a {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    transition: opacity var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .mission-link a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .mission-inner {
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .mission-body-block {
      padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .mission-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .mission-body-block {
      padding-left: 0;
      border-left: none;
    }
  }
</style>
